  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701830/extras/dbf1b98929f925e871cf87326df169d9.avif?t=1662970556\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Tangent Rush is a casual sidescroller with challenging gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701830/extras/e984dca772cfc8b4f83b3d486d464a64.poster.avif?t=1662970556\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701830/extras/e984dca772cfc8b4f83b3d486d464a64.webm?t=1662970556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701830/extras/e984dca772cfc8b4f83b3d486d464a64.mp4?t=1662970556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game is easy to pick up since you will only need your mouse to play the game.<br><br><strong>Challenging gameplay</strong><br>Levels will get harder the further you progress. New obstacles and challenges await you after completing another level.<br><br><strong>Online leaderboards</strong><br>Break your own records and compete for the highest leaderboard ranking!",
